I8CA4Q">Trịnh Sâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-th%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BB%A9-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-S%C3%B9ng-Thao/poem-oGxIQaP50ryYbR2GVVt1eA">Tứ thiếu bảo Trần Sùng Thao - 賜少保陳崇韜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B9ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-0stQjCT1gq_a6xH28mb1ow">Tương phùng hành - 相逢行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Hi%E1%BB%87u/V%E1%BB%8B-Th%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-fcKWtH-JN268WB_zKyvfdg">Vị Thành thiếu niên hành - 渭城少年行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Hi%E1%BB%87u/author-MRkAoTgdrsRPtV8a7n8AAw">Thôi Hiệu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
